* corners.lib — HSPICE library sections (used by top-lib.sp)

.lib TT
.model nch_tt nmos level=1 vto=0.7
.model pch_tt pmos level=1 vto=-0.7
.endl TT

.lib FF
.model nch_ff nmos level=1 vto=0.6
.model pch_ff pmos level=1 vto=-0.6
.endl FF

.lib SS
.model nch_ss nmos level=1 vto=0.8
.model pch_ss pmos level=1 vto=-0.8
.endl SS
